## CLI tools

| Command | What it does |
|---------|-------------|
| `tq-serve` | OpenAI-compatible inference server |
| `tq-compare` | Side-by-side output: baseline vs TurboQuant |
| `tq-bench` | Needle-in-haystack recall at increasing context lengths |

```bash
# Compare outputs side by side
tq-compare --model ./models/gemma4-e4b-4bit --prompt "What is entropy?" --key-bits 4

# Needle-in-haystack: does the model recall a fact buried in a long document?
tq-bench --model ./models/gemma4-e4b-4bit --lengths 512 1024 4096 8192

# Memory benchmark
tq-serve --model ./models/gemma4-e4b-4bit --benchmark --prompt-len 1024
```

